quran[12{c,v,t}:
97,1,hum ne iss ( quran ) ko shab qader mein nazil kya hai
97,2,aur tum kya jano ke shab qader kya hai ?
97,3,shab qader hazaar mahino se ziyada behtar hai
97,4,farishtay aur rooh uss mein apne Rab ke azan se har hukum le kar utartay hain
97,5,woh raat sara sar salamti hai tulu Fajar taq
98,1,ahal kitaab aur mushriqeen mein se jo log kafir thay ( woh apne kufar se ) baz anay walay nah thay jab taq ke un ke paas Daleel roshan nah aa jaye
98,2,( yani ) Allah ki taraf se aik rasool jo pak saheefay parh kar sunaye
98,3,jin mein bilkul raast aur durust tahreerein likhi hui hon
98,4,pehlay jin logon ko kitaab di gayi thi unn mein tafarruqa barpaa nahi howa magar iss ke baad ke unn ke paas ( raah raast ) ka bayan wazeh aa chuka tha
98,5,"aur unn ko iss ke siwa koi ilm nahi diya gaya tha ke Allah ki bandagi karen apne deen ko uss ke liye khalis kar ke, bilkul yaksu ho kar, aur namaz qaim karen aur zkoh den yahi nihayat sahih o durust deen hai"
98,6,"ahal kitaab aur mushriqeen mein se jin logon ne kufar kya hai woh yaqeenan jahannum ki aag mein jayen ge aur hamesha is mein rahen ge, yeh log bad tareen Khalaique hain"
98,7,"jo log imaan le aeye aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye, woh yaqeenan behtareen Khalaique hain"
